# The site's generated command catalog is emitted by packages/site/scripts/gen-catalog.mjs as
# JSON.stringify(…,2)+"\n" and byte-guarded by test/catalog.test.mjs (spec 005). Prettier's JSON
# collapsing would fight the generator and churn the file, so it is excluded like the other
# committed build artefacts above.
packages/site/src/data/catalog.json
# The site's live widget-demo assets (spec 011) — copies of the committed widget HTML above plus
# each widget's fixture as JSON, emitted by packages/site/scripts/gen-widget-demos.mjs into
# public/ on every dev/build. They are git-ignored, but Prettier does not read nested .gitignore
# files, so without this entry `format:check` would check (and reject) the copied widget HTML for
# exactly the reason the plugins/marvin/widgets/ entry above exists.
packages/site/public/widget-demos/
# The site's pipeline-tour recordings (spec 012) — asciicast files plus a copy of the asciinema
# vendor stylesheet, emitted by packages/site/scripts/gen-casts.mjs into public/ on every dev/build.
# Git-ignored, but Prettier does not read nested .gitignore files, so without this entry
# `format:check` would reject both the JSONL casts and the vendor CSS. Same reason as the entry
# above; the CSS half is exactly why `plugins/marvin/widgets/` is listed too.
packages/site/public/casts/
# Its committed manifest, emitted as JSON.stringify(…,2)+"\n" and byte-guarded by
# test/casts.test.mjs — excluded for the same reason catalog.json is: Prettier's JSON formatting
# would fight the generator and churn the file on every format run.
packages/site/src/data/casts.json
# The OpenGraph card manifest (spec 014), emitted by packages/site/scripts/gen-og.mjs as
# JSON.stringify(…,2)+"\n" — excluded for the same reason as the two manifests above. The cards
# themselves need no entry: Prettier infers no parser for .png and leaves them alone, which is also
# why the 101 committed widget visual baselines do not break format:check.
packages/site/src/data/og.json

